These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, juice, coffee
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person drinking coffee##7
3. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Beverage   | juice | fanta | coffee | milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, card-games, magic-tricks, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is traveling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | fishing | traveling | magic-tricks | card-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, yellow, white, amber
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
2. the person who likes amber is somewhere between the person who likes white and the person who likes yellow##7
3. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person who likes amber##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |  2   |    3    |   4    |
| Color   | fuchsia | yellow | amber | white |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, lizard
1. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the frog##7
2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
3. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet   | hamster | bird | lizard | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, handball, golf, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
4. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is volleyball##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Sport   | golf | tennis | handball | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
House: futuristic, ranch-style, tower, gothic-revival
1. the futuristic house is somewhere between the gothic-revival house and the ranch-style house##7
2. the tower house is somewhere between the futuristic house and the gothic-revival house##7
3. the tower house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
4. the tower house is somewhere to the right of the gothic-revival house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| House   | gothic-revival | tower | futuristic | ranch-style |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-7::.
