.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, january, may, april
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in may##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4    |
| Birthday   | may | august | april | january |

