.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, april, november, february
1. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
2. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in february##7
3. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2    |      3      |  4  |
| Birthday   | november | february | april | december |

 